To be put at a huge disadvantage even though you won the MOST GAMES out of 162 games because of the outcome of a fan voted game (One game as compared to 162) is maybe the most idiotic thing I have ever heard.  Ya..That's fair.<br>
<br>
Grr..Just talking about it pisses me off.<br>
